data.meta_description: The Moisture Festival includes an amazing array of performers. See the list below to view an archive of our Comedy/Variete performers.

ARCHIVE: COMEDY/VARIETÉ PERFORMERS

These are some of the artists who have graced the Moisture Festival’s stages over the years. For a list of artists who will be appearing at this year’s festival, click here.

To book an artist for your event, please contact them directly. Opening their bio will, in most cases, provide a website link.

Please note that the biographies that appear on this page have not been updated since the artist last appeared at Moisture Festival, which in some cases may have been many years ago. Therefore, some of these acts may no longer be performing, and some links to the performers’ websites may no longer be current.
